metadata.name: Karasu Tengu
metadata.description:
The Daimyos are handcrafted 1/1 NFTs from the Oni Ronin universe.

Each one was developed by a collector working in tandem with Big Head Club and Maldoror the Creative Director and Artist for the project.


To get your own Daimyo, collect one of each shade of the fallen ronin and send them to "roninhell.eth". 

Then email "Mack at Bighead.club" to begin your journey of co-creation.
